title: The Room Rifftrax.avi
description:
The Room exists as actual documented proof that just because you are an actor doesn't mean you know how to make movies. Join Mike, Kevin and Bill as they guide us through the incomprehensible film that is the Room.

Note: I saw the previous mix that was put up and didn't bother posting my own. Then today I noticed it had vanished, a pity as it's awesome. As I always ask, donate/buy from the gents at rifftrax.com to keep these coming.
